## Description
<h2>Digital Fusion 2.5 Evaluation</h2>

<p>The Digital Fusion Standard Evaluation was created to allow you the opportunity to explore eyeon Software's Digital Fusion compositing software. You may not use this evaluation for commercial work or professional training purposes.</p>

<p>This evaluation version will stamp all rendered files with a travelling logo, and all preview images will contain a large 'DF' stamped into the foreground of the image.</p>

<p>We have included three tutorials, and a small selection of tips and tricks from our website, to help you get started learning Digital Fusion. More help can be obtained by accessing the Help from the menu once Digital Fusion is running on your system.</p>

<p>The Fusion 2.5 content is saved to:</p>
<ul>
<li>Reactor:/Deploy/Bin/Eyeon Legacy/Digital Fusion 2.5/eyeon/DF252Eval-Intel.exe</li>
<li>Reactor:/Deploy/Docs/Eyeon Legacy/Digital Fusion 2.5 Tutorials/tutorials.zip</li>
</ul>
